g.text: 1. Reduce the overlapping of each part
Why dose the overlapping happened in primitive.js?
Through the process of generating abstract images, we can find:
1. It try to fit the whole image rather than the component(like the face, the ear...)
so maybe we can make a semantic segmentation and then fit in every component.
2. It use the tiny primitive to describe the details, but we actually dont want details,
shrink or control the primitive's size maybe a good way.
1. We should find the visual characterstics fist,
1. Humans possess a remarkable capacity to recognize and manipulate abstract structure,
which is especially apparent in the domain of geometry.
